{
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/((?!api/).*)", "destination": "/index.html" }
  ]
}
If you also have buildCommand/outputDirectory/framework keys already in there, keep them and just add the rewrites array alongside:

{
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/((?!api/).*)", "destination": "/index.html" }
  ],
  "buildCommand": "npm run build",
  "outputDirectory": "dist",
  "framework": "vite"
}